race.description: Ladbrokes Srm In Multis 1-4 Win Heat 2
race.comment: EADER (6) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (20.65) last time out at this track. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Sure to be about the mark. WHY A MACIE (1) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fifth (24.19) at Casino. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Better than last start and can bounce back. WHERE'S THE BOSS (8) recorded his 3rd career win last time at Casino, scoring by 3.5 lengths (16.96). Some good form is emerging from his last run. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. BUGATTI STEP (3) is worth consideration after filling a hole last start.
